titles.title: Electing a Member to a certain standing committee of the House of Representatives.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

bill.summary: 5/24/2007--Passed House without amendment. (This measure has not been amended since it was introduced. The summary of that version is repeated here.) Elects a named Majority Member to the House Committee on House Administration, including as Chairman.
